title: NOBLE CAUSES 039-040 (2009) (Minutemen-Captain John)
description:
Noble Causes #39 and #40, courtesy of Captain John of the Minutemen and some site I found yesterday. Requested by binderguy1. If you'd like to know the URL of my new favorite site for old, moderately obscure scans, shoot me a PM on the SuprBay forum. (Same user ID as here.)
